Requirements:

- Go 1.4: http://golang.org/doc/install

- libgit2 0.23: https://libgit2.github.com

- make 3.7 or greater: https://www.gnu.org/software/make/


Installation:

- Install library dependencies using `make bootstrap`, which fetches the necessary components via `go get`

- Run `make` to build the project, and `make install` to install it
